Log:
  merge r193027, r193557, r192900, r193028: fix trailing-slash symlink bug

  PR:		kern/21768

Modified:
  stable/7/sys/   (props changed)
  stable/7/sys/contrib/pf/   (props changed)
  stable/7/sys/kern/vfs_lookup.c
